NK010(tha)008:1: spros med rgyun gyi rnal 'byor bzhugs /
NK010(tha)008:2: gdan gsum lus kyi phur bu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK010(tha)008:3: lung a nu yo ga dang mthun par lus dkyil la brten nas phur pa bsgrub pa ni /
NK010(tha)008:4: skyabs sems sngon du byas la /
NK010(tha)008:6: sems dang yid dang rnam shes nyid //
NK010(tha)008:7: de nyid las ni 'khrul nas btab //
NK010(tha)008:8: rnam rtog bag chags bsreg pa'i phyir //
NK010(tha)008:9: bdag gi lus ni gzhal yas khang //
NK010(tha)008:11: rang lus 'dom gang gru bzhi ni //
NK010(tha)008:12: dur khrod gzhal yas khang du bsam //
NK010(tha)008:13: gru bzhi pa la kha dog lnga //
NK010(tha)008:14: dri ma nag po'i bee d+aur sngo //
NK010(tha)008:15: rtsa chen ljang gu mar gad mdog /
NK010(tha)008:16: khrag gi pad+ma r+aa ga dmar //
NK010(tha)008:17: tshil bu ser po gser ltar snang //
NK010(tha)008:18: rus pa dkar po shel dngul mdog /
NK010(tha)008:19: lnga yi rtsig pa rab tu mdzes //
NK010(tha)008:20: sgal tshig gdung gi rang bzhin la //
NK010(tha)008:21: rkang brgyad ka ba brgyad yin no //
NK010(tha)008:22: thur ma lcam la rtsib ma dral //
NK010(tha)008:23: rtsa yi d+r+wa bas rab 'brel zhing //
NK010(tha)008:24: mgo bo'i tshangs sgo shel ltar dkar //
NK010(tha)008:25: mig g.yas lho sgo gser ltar ser //
NK010(tha)008:26: mig g.yon byang sgo mar gad ljang //
NK010(tha)008:27: nub kyi chu sgo pad ltar dmar //
NK010(tha)008:28: 'og gi spu nag smin ma dang //
NK010(tha)008:29: skra rnams sgo yi rgyan yin no //
NK010(tha)008:30: rkang lag sen mo'i phreng ba rnams //
NK010(tha)008:31: mu tig d+r+wa ba phyed pas mdzes //
NK010(tha)008:32: tshigs mdud rin chen pha gu la //
NK010(tha)008:33: pags pa 'dod yon lha mos mdzes //
NK010(tha)008:34: dur khrod gzhal yas mdzes pa der //
NK010(tha)008:35: kun gzhi'i rnam shes gnas gyur pa //
NK010(tha)008:36: dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu ni //
NK010(tha)008:37: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung //
NK010(tha)008:38: dgod dang gshe dang 'jigs pa dang //
NK010(tha)008:39: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba ste //
NK010(tha)008:40: zhal dang phyag mtshan cir yang ston //
NK010(tha)008:41: yid kyi rnam shes gnas gyur pa //
NK010(tha)008:43: sgo lnga'i rnam shes gnas gyur pa //
NK010(tha)008:44: sras mchog rigs lnga yum dang bcas //
NK010(tha)008:45: gzugs kyi phur po rnam par rgyal //
NK010(tha)008:46: tshor ba gshin rje gshed po nyid //
NK010(tha)008:49: rnam shes khro rgyal h+aum k+aa ra //
NK010(tha)008:50: sa ni dbyug pa sngon po ste //
NK010(tha)008:51: chu ni mi g.yo mgon po la //
NK010(tha)008:52: me ni gzhan gyi mi thub pa //
NK010(tha)008:53: rlung ni khams gsum rnam rgyal te //
NK010(tha)008:54: nam mkha' khro rgyal stobs po che //
NK010(tha)008:55: skye mched yum bcu'i ngo bo ste //
NK010(tha)008:56: rnam par rtog pa khra phyag la //
NK010(tha)008:57: nyon mongs sgo ma bzhi nyid do //
NK010(tha)008:59: rdo rje gzhon nu'i rig 'dzin rnams //
NK010(tha)008:60: srid pa rdo rjer grub mdzod cig /
NK010(tha)008:61: srid pa rdo rje phur pa'i lha //
NK010(tha)008:62: ye shes khro bo grub par mdzod //
NK010(tha)008:63: bskyed du med de ye nas yin //
NK010(tha)008:64: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big nan bam h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)008:69: gsol ba'i zas ni ci yang rung //
NK010(tha)008:70: dang por ram yam kham gis sbyangs //
NK010(tha)008:71: a dkar 'od dang bcas pa las //
NK010(tha)008:73: 'od zer don gnyis byang chub sems //
NK010(tha)008:74: ye shes bdud rtsir gnyis med bstim //
NK010(tha)008:75: a mri ta yi gsang sngags kyis //
NK010(tha)008:76: 'od zhu bdud rtsi chen por gyur //
NK010(tha)008:77: sa ma ya a mri ta +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)008:78: lag pa ye shes hom gzar gyis //
NK010(tha)008:79: kha ni hom khung gzhal yas su //
NK010(tha)008:80: dbyings dang ye shes mchod par 'bul //
NK010(tha)008:81: mnyam pa'i sgrub rdzas yongs su dag /
NK010(tha)008:82: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK010(tha)008:83: longs spyod lnga ldan bdud rtsi mchog /
NK010(tha)008:84: gnyis med yongs su dag par bsngo //
NK010(tha)008:85: gnyis su med pa'i mchod pa yin //
NK010(tha)008:86: sku gsung thugs su rnam par dag /
NK010(tha)008:87: dman pa'i zas la bza' mi bya //
NK010(tha)008:88: btung ba t+r+aam las m+aa kir bsam //
NK010(tha)008:89: sbom po dbang mo thabs shes kyis //
NK010(tha)008:91: de bzhin gos dang rgyan gnas khang //
NK010(tha)008:92: dbang po lnga yi longs spyod kun //
NK010(tha)008:93: tha mal snang bas ma yin par //
NK010(tha)008:94: 'dod yon sgyu ma lta bu ru //
NK010(tha)008:95: dmigs nas yongs grub dkyil 'khor mchod //
NK010(tha)008:96: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs 'gyur //
